name: Fibonacci Words
statement: Input The input consists of a single string of uppercase letters A-Z. The length of the string is between 1 and 10 characters, inclusive. Output Output " YES " or " NO ". Examples Input HELP Output YES Input AID Output NO Input MARY Output NO Input ANNA Output YES Input MUG Output YES Input CUP Output NO Input SUM Output YES Input PRODUCT Output NO
inputFormat: The input consists of a single string of uppercase letters A-Z. The length of the string is between 1 and 10 characters, inclusive.
